Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.73,0:22:09.23,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}INSIDE  IDENTITY
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.23,0:22:12.03,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}我的棲身之地在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.16,0:22:24.67,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}誤解令人感到害羞什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.75,0:22:27.25,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}率真令人難以忍受什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.38,0:22:29.59,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}無論他人怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.59,0:22:32.47,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}我也不知到底「正確」為何物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.51,0:22:35.09,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}強迫自己去習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.30,0:22:37.68,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}一成不變的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.72,0:22:40.43,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}將沉淪的種種個性
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.52,0:22:42.64,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}啃食飲盡  唾棄嘲笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.68,0:22:47.27,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}希望你能理解這樣的我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.36,0:22:52.61,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}欲言又止
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.69,0:22:57.57,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}連思考「為什麼誰都無法理解我」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.70,0:23:02.66,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}都已成為一種奢侈了嗎？了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.87,0:23:07.96,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}多愁善感的太陽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.04,0:23:10.67,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}釋放出過多的熱量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.75,0:23:13.09,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}把我曬得快不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.21,0:23:18.18,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}按耐不住吶喊的衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.34,0:23:24.18,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}不顧一切地渴求IDENTITY
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.18,0:23:26.64,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}INSIDE  MY  FEELING
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.73,0:23:29.23,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}INSIDE  MY  JUSTICE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.27,0:23:31.77,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}千萬別妨礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.86,0:23:33.82,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}我的棲身之地在哪裡？
